---
import Layout from '../../Base.astro';
import SimpleHero from '../../components/SimpleHero.astro';
import FeaturedArticles from '../../components/FeaturedArticles.astro';
import ServicesRelatedWork from '../../components/ServicesRelatedWork.astro';
import '../../styles/pages/_services-list.scss';
---

<Layout
  title="Central Florida Website Design & Development Services"
  description="Our web design and development team can help you increase sales by providing optimized sites that convert visitors into lifelong customers."
>
  <SimpleHero
    tagline="Content Creation Services"
    title="Website Design & Development"
    description="Our web design and development team can help you increase sales by providing optimized sites that convert visitors into lifelong customers."
    lottieFile="web-design.json"
  />
  <div class="service-body">
    <div class="wrapper wrapper--narrow">
      <h2>Why design & development matter</h2>
      <p>
        Your website is more than a digital presence—it is a system that supports how your business communicates, builds
        trust, and drives action.
      </p>
      <p>
        Effective websites are not defined by design alone. Structure, content, performance, and usability must work
        together to guide visitors toward clear outcomes. When those elements are misaligned, even visually strong sites
        underperform.
      </p>
      <p>
        We approach every project with intention—ensuring your site is easy to navigate, built for real user behavior,
        and aligned with your business goals.
      </p>
      <h2>Web applications</h2>
      <p>
        Some businesses require more than a marketing website. When your operations, data, or customer experience demand
        it, custom web applications provide the flexibility and control that off-the-shelf tools cannot.
      </p>
      <p>
        We design and develop web-based tools that streamline processes, surface meaningful data, and create more
        interactive user experiences—all within a system that is built specifically for how your business operates.
      </p>

      <ul>
        <li>Custom Website Development</li>
        <li>Web Applications & Internal Tools</li>
        <li>Dashboards & Data Interfaces</li>
        <li>Interactive Data Visualizations</li>
        <li>UI/UX Enhancements & Motion</li>
      </ul>
      <p><a href="/contact/" class="button button--green">Let's Talk</a></p>
    </div>
    <ServicesRelatedWork tag={66} />
  </div>
  <FeaturedArticles />
</Layout>
